        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>The HVAC water drain tube in certain International&#174; 4000, 7000, 8000 HPV models built between
                    September 1, 2003 and August 15, 2005 may not function correctly and under some conditions allows
                    water to drip into the cab.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
